{"tid":432054,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一年一度連登曬命post  快啲入黎","createTime":"2017-10-11T07:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T08:33:48.000Z","uid":151605,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9e2a7a0932d71c0fe73540501b2099439f6c3873","tid":432054,"uid":151605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T07:30:56.000Z","msg":"咁多位 連登仔 相信成日睇連登都見到好多有錢巴絲 而家係時候啦 集合晒 連登咁多人 講下自己幾有錢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我講先 利申唔算有錢 中產仔一個<br />\n屋企住居屋 一家四口 屋企得老豆同家姐二個返工<br />\n家姐份工好普通 萬幾蚊 好小 唔講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老豆做電個啲 一個月 50000咁上下 而我未出黎做野做讀緊書 得閒做下pt 家族有村屋 6間租緊俾人 得閒收下租 大約一個月 30000到 加埋晒 （村屋唔同市區樓）咁 叫做唔擔心衣食住行 屋企人會買玩股票 但我唔識 薪家 我自己就 30000幾  自己算大洗個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 家姐就唔知 應該多我啲 佢都好大洗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 阿媽之前返工草落 200 300萬咁上下 老豆應該接近千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  快啲入黎講下啦大家 我講真 唔係吹出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5543bc3354d6cc2b9d77cd25353dd0df5c907d96","tid":432054,"uid":128101,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T07:34:42.000Z","msg":"老豆係上海有兩個商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55554d358a8a9dbfd219c20487670777695f655c","tid":432054,"uid":151605,"l